alerts.description:
...HIGH RIP CURRENT RISK NOW IN EFFECT THROUGH MONDAY EVENING...
* WHAT...Dangerous rip currents.
* WHERE...Coastal Broward, Coastal Palm Beach and Coastal Miami-
Dade Counties.
* WHEN...Through Monday evening.
* IMPACTS...Rip currents can sweep even the best swimmers away
from shore into deeper water.

alerts.sender_name: Agencija Republike Slovenije za okolje (ARSO vreme)
alerts.description: Thunderstorms are possible, accompanied by local intense precipitation and gusty winds.  Intense local showers with wind blasts and lightning strikes are possible. Torrential watercourses may rise quickly. Rainwater floods are possible.
